Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:22.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僕ら行先も知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:26.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}流され 戦ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}離れ離れになって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}空っぽになっても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}また背負い込んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}去っていったあなたの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僕を支えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:47.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}追い続けたら見える新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}限界だなんて幻想だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}覆してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:03.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}奪われようと 失くしてはいない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}胸の中で生きていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:10.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:15.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この居場所を終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.78,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我們如同落葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.24,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}飄零於水面上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:22.01,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}漂泊不知去處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:26.22,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}隨波逐流而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.37,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便天涯兩隔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.97,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便身無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.25,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只得背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.48,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}念你如初
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.77,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}前行不止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:47.41,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}不斷追尋 新世界就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.27,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}極限云云 不過是幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.90,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.29,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}將一切反轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:03.27,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便被奪走也不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.27,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只要你還活在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:10.95,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:15.80,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我就不會容許這片土地淪陷
